==Treatment==
===Surgery===
The treatment of choice is complete surgical removal (''i.e.,'' complete resection).<ref>{{cite journal |author=Tapper D, Lack EE |title=Teratomas in infancy and childhood. A 54-year experience at the Children's Hospital Medical Center |journal=Ann. Surg. |volume=198 |issue=3 |pages=398–410 |year=1983 |pmid=6684416 |pmc=1353316 |url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC1353316/pdf/annsurg00127-0168.pdf}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal 
